<li id="cite_note-16"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-16">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFCoupe2000" class="citation news cs1">Coupe, Lawrence (27 November 2000). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.pnreview.co.uk/cgi-bin/scribe?item_id=734;hilite=Ivo%20Mosley">"The Moronic Inferno"</a>. <i>PN Review 136</i>. Vol.&#160;27.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=PN+Review+136&amp;rft.atitle=The+Moronic+Inferno&amp;rft.volume=27&amp;rft.date=2000-11-27&amp;rft.aulast=Coupe&amp;rft.aufirst=Lawrence&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pnreview.co.uk%2Fcgi-bin%2Fscribe%3Fitem_id%3D734%3Bhilite%3DIvo%2520Mosley&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAnti-intellectualism" class="Z3988"></span></span>
